{"tid":759863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普：沙基利唔正常！","createTime":"2018-07-29T04:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T14:01:56.000Z","uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2adf1e468959bb6a47e480822faf687bcebf20f","tid":759863,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=%2BE7Kq8wY7GpSYtDHNsGSHBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=99c5d797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】梳頓沙基利首次為利物浦上陣，就以一記倒掛金球作為見面禮，領隊高普以「不正常」來形容該瑞士中場的演出。<br />\n<br />\n「以一名只是適應了4天的球員而言，踢出這種風格，是不正常。」高普賽後自然對以金球助球隊埋齋的新兵梳頓沙基利（Xherdan Shaqiri）讚不絕口：「這是比我所預期更加出色。」<br />\n<br />\n這場在美國上演的國冠盃雙紅會，比賽至82分鐘，以後備身份首度為紅軍披甲的沙基利接應活特本左路傳中，施展倒掛，以一個妙絕入球助紅軍湊成4:1大捷。「不過今天這場比賽，倒是很容易融入隊中。」高普續說。<br />\n<br />\n高普讚賞的還有前鋒史杜列治：「我很喜歡他，首先作為球員，他很出眾。當我加盟時，我為與他共事感到興奮，之後，他受傷困擾，然後改善不少。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"e9e88395140ba068a6cbb41246e7dd9fa102ac91","tid":759863,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"要贏英超R連了。"},{"pid":"54a81f1dcf64846a94673e70d17e5df8c9555719","tid":759863,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"矮仔易倒掛"},{"pid":"037ad8b536ac8dc12763cd0f457d983f2b6c2a45","tid":759863,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a81f1dcf64846a94673e70d17e5df8c9555719","tid":759863,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"矮仔易倒掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f663901cb8725876a3eec029f070d5f3a48492","tid":759863,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4435eda94204e7cabd1da84f3fea32107a7cb5ea","tid":759863,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a81f1dcf64846a94673e70d17e5df8c9555719","tid":759863,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"矮仔易倒掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"XX ?"}]}